css
.maze-corridor {
  width: 200px;
  height: 100px;
  position: relative;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(
    90deg,
    #555,
    #555 10px,
    transparent 10px,
    transparent 20px
  );

  /* Walls */
  &::before,
  &::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 10px;
    background: #555;
  }
  &::before { left: 0; }
  &::after { right: 0; }
}

This creates a basic corridor with textured walls using minimal CSS.
